description:
LBM hla thar ber hetah hian : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BX4tFiUD224
He Nupui/Pasal zawn hla hi ABC Music group chuan 1983 khan Zosangliani Raltiang ram Cassette album phel a chan ve ah record in an lo release tawh a.  Tunah tlem a modified hnu in sak nawn leh a ni.
A phuah tu: Tawna (Za Tawn Eng). Phuah kum: 1983.
Tawna hi Burma ah chuan Salai Tawna, ABC tia hriat a ni a, Burma ram pum hriat musician, artist mi lar tak Zofate zinga kan neih chhhun mi pakhat a ni. Tawna Mizo hla phuah te zing an hriat lar deuh te:
-Tlai tla eng (C.Luri)
-Zawlkhawdi Tleitir (ABC-1983, Rebecca Saimawii)
-Tlawmngaihna hlu (ABC-1983, Lalrindiki Khiangte, Mizoram Various Artists) etc.
